    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100种战争核心玩法是有多种不同且有趣的模式，搭配多个地图，武器，随机性能让你每一局都是新奇刺激的体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超多不同有趣的规则</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种武器 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种多样的地图</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有趣的剧情体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多个队伍竞争</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>七大关卡 可以无限成长</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>炸裂的射击快感</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>男主女主是这个世界仅存的人类 男主肩负着延续人类文明的责任 而女主却一心复仇，机器人与人的宿命殊途同归</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/fa3aebac03798b8a68eb4c88e5187f2c.poster.avif?t=1728995155\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/fa3aebac03798b8a68eb4c88e5187f2c.webm?t=1728995155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/fa3aebac03798b8a68eb4c88e5187f2c.mp4?t=1728995155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/a1e42e5a62ac95abf5990af6f3b5e4e8.poster.avif?t=1728995155\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/a1e42e5a62ac95abf5990af6f3b5e4e8.webm?t=1728995155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/a1e42e5a62ac95abf5990af6f3b5e4e8.mp4?t=1728995155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video cl